                            <h1 class="title">At Games Logistics</h1>
                            <h2>Accommodation</h2>
    <p>
        Accommodations in Sochi have been quite difficult to source, are generally of a lower standard than what we are accustomed to in Canada, and can be very expensive.
    </p>
    <p>
        CoSport/Jet Set is our official partner of Olympic tickets and accommodation packages. They will be offering accommodation packages for Sochi, however we have no indication of timelines or pricing. We do know that they will be targeting 3-Star and 4-Star properties. They will let COC know when they are ready to offer this by invitation only, at which point we will update family and friends. 
    </p>
    <p>
        Several accommodation brokers in Sochi have reserved blocks of rooms at various hotels to sell off to the general public. One company that the COC has worked with to book our own rooming needs is Trekking Hellas. Although they are not an official partner of the COC, they have been helpful with this process. Below you will find their contact information. 
    </p>
